17... d5 18. exd5 cxd5 $15) 18. Nc4 (18. Rhe1 $142 $5 $11 {and White hangs on})
18... d5 $17 19. Nxe5 $2 (19. exd5 $142 e4 20. Qg3 cxd5 21. Na3 $17) 19... Nxe4
$4 {an unfortunate move that relinquishes the win.} (19... a3 $142 {Black has
a promising position} 20. b3 Nxe5 21. dxe5 Nxe4 $19) 20. Nxc6 $16 Qa6 (20...
Nxc3 21. Qxc3 Qb6 22. Ne7+ Kh8 23. Nxd5 $16) 21. Ne7+ (21. Bxd5 Nxc3 22. Qxc3
Rae8 $18) 21... Kh8 $16 22. Bxd5 (22. Bb4 $142 $5 Qb7 23. Nxd5 $16) 22... Nxc3
