pawn: e3} 33. Kh2 Qf6 34. g3 h5 35. h4 (35. Qe2 g6 $14) 35... g6 36. b3 $4 {
weakening the position} (36. Kg1 $142 $11 {the only rescuing move}) 36... cxb3
$19 37. Nxb3 (37. Qb2 $142 Bd5 38. e4 fxe4 39. Nxb3 $19) 37... Qc6 $4 {letting
the wind out of his own sails} (37... Qxc3 $142 {a pity that Black didn't try
this} 38. Nd2 Bd5 $19) 38. Qb2 (38. Qd2 Qc4 39. Qd8+ Kh7 40. Qe7+ Kh6 41. Qg5+
Kh7 42. Qe7+ Kh6 43. Qg5+ Kg7 44. Qe7+ Kh6 $11) 38... Qd5 (38... Qc4 $142 $5
39. Kg1 Bd5 $17) 39. Nd4 $11 Kh7 40. Qf2 Qc4 {Black threatens to win material:
Qc4xc3} 41. Qb2 $4 (41. Nf3 $142 $11 {was necessary}) 41... Qf1 (41... Qf1 42.
Nf3 Bxf3 43. g4 fxg4 44. f5 g5 45. hxg5 h4 46. g6+ Kh6 47. Qb3 Qf2#) 0-1

