{A40: Unusual replies to 1 d4} 1. d4 e6 2. Nf3 b6 3. e3 Bb7 4. Be2 $146 (4. Bd3
f5 5. O-O Nf6 6. c4 Be7 (6... Bd6 7. Nc3 O-O 8. Ne5 (8. Qe2 Ne4 9. Bxe4 fxe4
10. Nd2 Qg5 11. Ndxe4 Bxe4 12. Nxe4 Bxh2+ 13. Kxh2 Qh4+ 14. Kg1 Qxe4 15. f3 Qg6
16. e4 Nc6 17. Be3 d5 18. cxd5 exd5 19. Rac1 Rf7 20. Qb5 Ne7 21. Rxc7 Rd8 22.
Rxa7 dxe4 {Mamedjarova,Z (2234)-Hoang,T (2482) Khanty-Mansiysk 2010 1-0 (67)})
8... Bxe5 9. dxe5 Ng4 10. Be2 Nxe5 11. b3 Rf6 12. f4 Rg6 13. e4 Ng4 14. Bf3 Bc6
15. exf5 exf5 16. Nd5 a5 17. Ba3 Kh8 18. Ne7 Rf6 19. Bxg4 fxg4 20. Qxg4 d6 21.
