c5 8. Qe2 Ne4 9. Ne1 O-O 10. f3 Nxd2 11. Bxd2 Nc6 12. Bc3 Bf6 13. Nc2 Qe7 14.
Qd2 f4 15. Be4 fxe3 16. Qxe3 cxd4 17. Nxd4 Qc5 18. Bxc6 Bxc6 19. b3 b5 20. cxb5
Bxb5 21. Rf2 Rac8 {Piankov,E (2324)-Hasangatin,R (2498) Tabor 2010 1/2-1/2 (31)
}) 7... O-O 8. Ba3 Bxa3 9. Nxa3 Qe7 10. Nb5 d6 11. Rc1 a6 12. Nc3 Nbd7 13. Bb1
g6 14. Qe2 Ne4 15. Nxe4 Bxe4 16. Bxe4 fxe4 17. Nd2 Nf6 18. b4 a5 {Bellon Lopez,
J (2364)-Eriksson,K (2177) Tylosand 2015 1-0 (32)}) 4... Nc6 5. O-O d5 6. b3
Bd6 7. Bb2 Nf6 8. c4 Qe7 9. Nc3 a6 {Prevents intrusion on b5} 10. a3 {Secures
b4} O-O 11. b4 dxc4 12. Bxc4 b5 {Black threatens to win material: b5xc4} 13.
Be2 Nd8 14. Rc1 e5 $2 (14... Nd5 15. Nxd5 Bxd5 16. Qc2 $11) 15. dxe5 (15. Nxb5
$5 e4 16. Nxd6 exf3 17. Nf5 $16) 15... Bxe5 16. Nxe5 Qxe5 17. Bf3 Qe7 18. Nd5 (
18. e4 Nc6 19. e5 Qxe5 $16) 18... Nxd5 $14 19. Bxd5 c6 (19... Bxd5 20. Qxd5 Ne6
21. Qc6 $14) 20. Bf3 Rc8 21. Qb3 (21. Qd4 Ne6 22. Qb6 Ng5 $16) 21... Ne6 (21...
c5 22. Bxb7 Nxb7 23. bxc5 Nxc5 24. Qb4 $11) 22. Rfd1 (22. Bg4 $5 $14) 22... c5
$11 23. Bxb7 {White forks: a6+c8} Qxb7 24. bxc5 Nxc5 25. Qc3 {White has a mate
threat} Ne6 26. Qe5 Rxc1 {Black has a mate threat} 27. Rxc1 b4 28. axb4 Qxb4
29. h3 h6 30. f4 Re8 31. Bc3 Qf8 32. Qa5 {White threatens to win material:
Qa5xa6} Ra8 33. Be5 Qe7 34. Kh2 Qb7 35. Qc3 (35. f5 Ng5 $14) 35... Qe4 $11 36.
Ra1 Kh7 37. Ra3 f6 38. Bd6 Qd5 (38... a5 39. Rxa5 Rxa5 40. Qxa5 Qxe3 41. Qf5+
Kh8 42. Qb1 $11) 39. Bb4 (39. Qc2+ Kg8 40. Rxa6 Rxa6 41. Qc8+ Kh7 42. Qxa6 h5
$16) 39... Nd8 (39... Qe4 $5 $11) 40. Qc2+ $14 Kh8 41. Qg6 Qf7 {Black
threatens to win material: Qf7xg6} 42. Qe4 {White threatens to win material:
Qe4xa8} Qb7 {Black threatens to win material: Qb7xe4} 43. Qe8+ Kh7 44. Qe4+ $4
{what a pity, victory was in sight} (44. Ba5 $14) 44... g6 (44... Qxe4 $142 {
and Black has it in the bag} 45. Bd2 Ne6 46. Be1 $19) 45. Rd3 $4 {stumbles
just before the finish line} (45. Qxb7+ $142 Nxb7 46. Rc3 $16) 45... Nf7 (45...
Qxe4 $142 {secures the win} 46. Rd7+ Kg8 $19) 46. Qe6 (46. Qxb7 Ra7 47. Qxa7
