(47... -- $140 48. Qxf7+ {Mate threat}) 48. Rd7 Ng5 49. fxg5 Qb8+ (49... Qxd7 {
a fruitless try to alter the course of the game} 50. Qxd7 Rg7 51. gxf6 Rg8 52.
Bd6+ Kh8 53. Be5 a5 54. f7+ Rg7 55. f8=Q+ Kh7 56. Qdxg7#) 50. Bd6+ (50. Bd6+
