15. exd5 Bd6 16. Bd2 $11) 15. f5 {White wins space} (15. Nxe7+ Qxe7 16. e5 Ne8
$14) 15... h6 {Secures g5} (15... Rfe8 16. b3 $11) 16. Bf4 (16. Nxe7+ Qxe7 17.
e5 Bxf3 18. exf6 Bxg2+ 19. Kxg2 Qxf6 $16) 16... Bc6 (16... Nxd5 $142 $5 {
is interesting} 17. exd5 Bd6 $11) 17. Nxe7+ $16 Qxe7 18. e5 Bxf3 19. exf6 Qe2
$4 {causes further problems for ?} (19... Bxg2+ $142 20. Kxg2 Qxf6 $16) 20.
Rxf3 (20. Qxf3 $142 {might be the shorter path} Qxf3 21. Rxf3 Kh7 22. fxg7 Kxg7
23. f6+ Kh7 $18) 20... Qxb2 (20... Rfe8 $18) 21. Raf1 Rfe8 (21... Qc3 {doesn't
get the cat off the tree} 22. Qxc3 dxc3 23. Rxc3 $18) 22. Rg3 Re2 (22... Qc3
23. Qd1 Qxc4 24. Rxg7+ Kh8 25. Bxh6 Re4 26. Be3 Rh4 27. Rf4 Rh6 28. Rg5 Qa4 29.
Qh5 Qd1+ 30. Qxd1 Rg8 31. Qh5 Rgg6 32. fxg6 Rxh5 33. g7+ Kh7 34. g8=Q+ Kh6 35.
Qg7#) 23. Rxg7+ Kh8 (23... Kf8 {doesn't get the bull off the ice} 24. Qf3 Rb8
25. Bd6+ Ke8 26. Qc6+ Kd8 27. Rg8+ Re8 28. Rxe8#) 24. Qg3 (24. Qh3 Qxa2 25.
Qxh6#) 24... Rc2 (24... Rxg2 {does not solve anything} 25. Qh4 Rxg7 26. fxg7+
Kg8 27. Qxh6 Qxh2+ 28. Bxh2 f6 29. Re1 Kf7 30. Qh7 Rg8 31. Qg6#) 25. Rh7+ $1 {
